messages.text: Hello? I found this phone in the cinema toilets. Is this Jason?
Hello! You’ve found my sister’s phone. She lost it earlier today.
I’ll tell her that someone found it! 😊 What’s your name?
Olivia. Or Liv
OK Liv. 😊 Where are you atm? So she can come and get it from you later?
I’m downstairs at the mall. Near the ice cream place
I’m not far from there actually! I might come and get it if that’s OK?
Yeah that’s cool I’m just hanging out
I’m queueing atm but I’ll be along in a bit
Where are you queueing?
The toy store upstairs...
Haha what are you buying?
Christmas present for my little brother
Aww cute! 😊 What are you getting him?
A teddy bear that looks like an astronaut
OMG that is so sweet. How old is he?
Yeah it is pretty cute haha. 😊 Quite tempted to keep it for myself...
Surely you must be too old for teddy bears :P
Maybe a little. You should see how awesome this bear is though
You’ll have to come and show me. ;)
Haha I will. 😊 He has all these flashing lights on his suit. I’m jealous
I bet your brother will love it!! :)
Do you have any siblings?
No, I’m an only child 😁
Lucky!! I have two siblings and I have to share everything
That must suck :P
It does. OMG this line is taking forever
I went past there earlier, it looked super busy :-/
Yeah and it still is. I’m not far from the front now though
Yay :D
I’m so hungry too ugh
Maybe when you come down here you should get some ice cream ;D
Maybe :P
Got to the front yet?
Nearly. There’s like two people in front of me
OMG this woman will not shut up. Leave the cashier alone!!
What’s she doing?
Apparently he used the wrong gift wrap or something stupid like that.
She’s being really rude to him
Oh no 😞
I’m going to tell her to leave him alone
:O
Jason to the rescue!!
What happened? Jason?
Haha it’s OK, she just got super mad
She totally lost it and just dumped all her shopping and left the store
What did you say to her?
Just told her to stop giving the guy such a hard time
I mean, it’s Christmas, he’s probably so busy all the time
Like, have some Christmas spirit :D
I bet she didn’t like that :P
Nope, she just yelled at me and left
That’s so good that you stood up for him though 😊
Haha I do try to be a stand-up guy
I bet he appreciated it
And finally it’s my turn to be served :D
Woo finally!
You still at the ice cream place?
Yeah I’m here 😊
Good, let me just get sorted and I’ll come meet you
OK I’m coming now! 😊
How should I know it’s you?
Look out for the weirdo with a massive teddy bear ;)
How can I recognize you?
I’m wearing a pink top. Sitting outside the ice cream place
OK I’m really close
Did you say you were outside? I can’t see you
Liv??
Did you leave?
Liv it’s not funny 😞 Where did you go?
Sorry!!
Where are you???
Sorry I didn’t realize it was you!! I freaked out
What do you mean?
I saw you coming!! I’ve seen you at school
I didn’t realize you were THAT Jason
Why is that bad??
Come on, at least tell me
It’s embarrassing
It can’t be that bad
And I do need that phone :P
OK
Do you remember a Christmas dance a few years ago
And a girl you didn’t really know asked you to dance
And you said no
I think so?? Why?
That was me 😞
OMG really?
Now I’m embarrassed
You laughed at me
😞 I’m sorry
Like you could have given me a chance, you didn’t have to be rude
I was like 14 and an idiot
I know better now
How come I don’t see you at school?
I tend to stay out of your way
I get embarrassed easily
I hate remembering it
I would have left the phone if I knew it was your sister’s
I think I can see you
What! No you can’t
You said you were wearing a pink top. Is that you in the sports store?
The one opposite the ice cream place
Don’t follow me!
Well I need that phone back
OK but that’s all
I’ll come out now
Well I want to say sorry too
To your face, not over text
Can I do that?
OK
Maybe you can let me make it up to you too 😊
How so?
Maybe you would let me take you on a date? 😊
To make up for me being a jerk
If that’s OK with you
Why?
Because I’m sorry
And you sound cute 😊
You kept me entertained in that line haha
Well. I guess one date couldn’t hurt 😊
That’s the spirit!! You going to come out of the store now?
OK. I’m coming 😊
